column2: SELECT count(*) g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_eqw, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_eqw, g.h_alpha_flux, g. h_alpha_eqw, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_eqw FROM SpecObj AS s JOIN GalSpecLine AS g ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE (s.class = &&& or s.class = &&&) AND g.sigma_balmer < #/# AND s.snmedian_g > # AND s.snmedian_r > # AND g.oiii_#_flux > # AND g.h_beta_flux > # AND g.h_alpha_flux > # AND g.nii_#_flux > # AND g.oiii_#_flux > #*g.oiii_#_flux_err AND g.h_beta_flux > #*g.h_beta_flux_err AND g.h_alpha_flux > #*g.h_alpha_flux_err AND g.nii_#_flux > #*g.nii_#_flux_err
